": "TR", "fieldwork": "Jun 11-18 2021", "electionDate": "2021-07-11", "respondents": 1008, "methodology": {"en": "Face-to-face interviews", "bg": "Интервю \"лице в лице\""}, "source": "https://www.actualno.com/society/trend-pet-sigurni-formacii-v-sledvashtija-parlament-news_1571780.html", "genre": "raw_attitudes", "residual": {"undecided": 19, "wontVote": null, "wontSay": null, "otherNamedMinor": null, "notes": "Stored notes: 81% decided / 19% undecided / 48% will-vote / minor parties (Bg patrioti 3.9, Vazr 2.3, Bg lyato 1.9, Lyav 1.1) match Trend's published structure."}}, {"id": "tr-2017-03-16", "agencyId": "TR", "fieldwork": "Mar 10-16 2017", "electionDate": "2017-03-26", "respondents": 1004, "methodology": {"en": "N/A", "bg": "N/A"}, "source": "N/A", "genre": "raw_attitudes", "residual": {"undecided": null, "wontVote": null, "wontSay": null, "otherNamedMinor": null, "notes": "Primary source reports 'Не подкрепям никого' = 3.1% among declared voters. Roughly 'two-thirds decided / one-fifth undecided' in commentary, no explicit % published. Other named minors: ABV-Movement21 2.6, New Republic 2.3, Yes Bulgaria 2.2."}}, {"id": "sh-2026-04-06", "agencyId": "SH", "fieldwork": "Apr 2-6 2026", "electionDate": "2026-04-19", "respondents": 800, "methodology": {"en": "N/A", "bg": "N/A"}, "source": "https://sovaharris.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Buletin_0426_page-0009-791x1024.jpg", "genre": "both_published", "residual": {"undecided": null, "wontVote": null, "wontSay": null, "otherNamedMinor": 3.7, "notes": "Agency bulletin page 9 (\"САМО СРЕД ГЛАСУВАЩИТЕ ЗА КОНКРЕТНА ПАРТИЯ/КОАЛИЦИЯ\") sums named shares + a single \"Друга / Не подкрепям никого\" line to 100%; the 3.7pp goes to that \"other/none\" bucket. Granular undecided breakdown not published in the same denominator."}}, {"id": "sh-2026-03-12", "agencyId": "SH", "fieldwork": "Mar 7-12 2026", "electionDate": "2026-04-19", "respondents": 1000, "methodology": {"en": "N/A", "bg": "N/A"}, "source": "https://sovaharris.com/политически-нагласи-в-българия-2/", "genre": "both_published", "residual": {"undecided": 19.3, "wontVote": 17, "wontSay": 0.8, "otherNamedMinor": null, "notes": "Per news.bg coverage of the Sova Harris release: Decided to vote 46.8%, will vote but undecided 19.3%, haven't decided whether to vote 16.1%, won't vote 17%, no response 0.8%. The 'wont_vote' here strictly refers to expressed non-participation; the 16.1% 'haven't decided whether to vote' could be added to undecided."}}, {"id": "sh-2025-06-11", "agencyId": "SH", "fieldwork": "Jun 9-11 2025", "electionDate": "2026-04-19", "respondents": 1000, "methodology": {"en": "Standardized face-to-face interview", "bg": "Стандартизирано интервю \"лице в лице\""}, "source": "https://www.bta.bg/bg/news/bulgaria/909924-prouchvane-na-sova-haris-sochi-che-informatsionnata-kampaniya-na-upravlyavash", "genre": "raw_attitudes", "residual": {"undecided": null, "wontVote": null, "wontSay": null, "otherNamedMinor": 10, "notes": "BTA reports ~10% for 'other parties'."}}, {"id": "sh-2024-10-24", "agencyId": "SH", "fieldwork": "Oct 11-17 2024", "electionDate": "2024-10-27", "respondents": 800, "methodology": {"en": "Standardized face-to-face interview", "bg": "Стандартизирано интервю \"лице в лице\""}, "source": "https://tvn.bg/sova-haris-povtarya-se-rezultatat-ot-izborite-prez-yuni/", "genre": "raw_attitudes", "residual": {"undecided": null, "wontVote": null, "wontSay": null, "otherNamedMinor": 1.8, "notes": "Primary mentions 42.3% completely-sure-to-vote, 57% understand high turnout importance. Synia Bulgaria 1.8% explicitly listed by agency."}}, {"id": "sh-2024-06-01", "agencyId": "SH", "fieldwork": "May 29 - Jun 3 2024", "electionDate": "2024-06-09", "respondents": 1000, "methodology": {"en": "Standardized face-to-face interview", "bg": "Стандартизирано интервю \"лице в лице\""}, "source": "https://www.marica.bg/tema-v-razvitie/izbori-2024/sova-haris-gerb-darpa-s-10-avans-fotofinish-za-vtoroto-mqsto-radev-shampion-po-reyting", 