undecided will trigger our proportional-redistribution rule, producing a 'decided voters' denominator that matches the official ЦИК basis."}}, {"id": "na-2009-07-05", "agencyId": "NA", "fieldwork": "2009", "electionDate": "2009-07-05", "respondents": null, "methodology": {"en": "General polling consensus", "bg": "Общ консенсус на проучванията"}, "source": "N/A"}, {"id": "na-2005-06-25", "agencyId": "NA", "fieldwork": "2005", "electionDate": "2005-06-25", "respondents": null, "methodology": {"en": "General polling consensus", "bg": "Общ консенсус на проучванията"}, "source": "N/A"}, {"id": "my-2026-04-13", "agencyId": "MY", "fieldwork": "Apr 4-13 2026", "electionDate": "2026-04-19", "respondents": 1002, "methodology": {"en": "N/A", "bg": "N/A"}, "source": "https://clubz.bg/173572", "genre": "raw_attitudes", "residual": {"undecided": null, "wontVote": null, "wontSay": null, "otherNamedMinor": 1.7, "notes": "Among those declaring they'll vote, 1.7% choose 'Не подкрепям никого'. Declared turnout intention: 50.7%. Methodology: face-to-face with tablets, MOE ±3.1 at 50%. Commissioned by Bulgarian National Radio. The clubz.bg coverage is the most direct contemporaneous press citation; agency's own post not yet found at myara.bg/en (likely behind a different slug)."}}, {"id": "my-2026-03-16", "agencyId": "MY", "fieldwork": "Mar 7-16 2026", "electionDate": "2026-04-19", "respondents": 809, "methodology": {"en": "N/A", "bg": "N/A"}, "source": "https://myara.bg/electoral-snapshot-march-2026-1681/", "genre": "raw_attitudes", "residual": {"undecided": null, "wontVote": null, "wontSay": null, "otherNamedMinor": 4.1, "notes": "Agency itemizes Сияние (Siyanie) at 2.3% and 'Не подкрепям никого' at 1.8% — these are missing from stored data. MOE ±3.5 at 50% shares. Agency explicitly states: 'не са прогноза за изборен резултат, а моментна снимка на електоралните нагласи' (not a forecast, a snapshot of electoral attitudes)."}}, {"id": "my-2026-02-15", "agencyId": "MY", "fieldwork": "Feb