ation, 15.6% will not vote, 1.8% no answer. Methodology: two-stage stratified sampling, MOE ±3.1% at 50%. Commissioned for use by various Bulgarian press."}}, {"id": "cam-2026-02-24", "agencyId": "CAM", "fieldwork": "Feb 17-24 2026", "electionDate": "2026-04-19", "respondents": 1010, "methodology": {"en": "N/A", "bg": "N/A"}, "source": "https://banker.bg/2026/02/26/czentar-analizi-marketing-5-partien-parlament/", "genre": "both_published", "residual": {"undecided": 33, "wontVote": 17.5, "wontSay": null, "otherNamedMinor": null, "notes": "Per banker.bg / dnes.dir.bg coverage of the CAM release: 35% decided voters, 33% undecided about party, 14% haven't decided whether to vote, 17.5% won't vote. CAM director Yuli Pavlov is the spokesperson. Stored shares match the 'raw electoral attitudes' figures — CAM ALSO publishes a forecast among decided voters (slightly different — leader 32.1% rather than the stored 33.7%) — see notes below."}}, {"id": "ar-2026-04-15", "agencyId": "AR", "fieldwork": "Apr 13-15 2026", "electionDate": "2026-04-19", "respondents": 1000, "methodology": {"en": "Stratified two-stage quota sample with face-to-face tablet (TAPI) interviewing at respondents’ homes. Self-funded by Alpha Research.", "bg": "Стратифицирана двустепенна извадка с квота по основните социално-демографски признаци. Пряко стандартизирано интервю с таблети (TAPI) по домовете на анкетираните. Самофинансирано от Алфа Рисърч."}, "source": "https://alpharesearch.bg/post/1047-obshtestveni-naglasi-na-finala-na-predizbornata-kampania.html", "genre": "forecast", "residual": {"undecided": null, "wontVote": 40, "wontSay": null, "otherNamedMinor": 2.6, "notes": "Stored notes claim 'Други 2.6%' added manually after publication. The primary post does not itemize 'Други' — it reports 72% chose pre-campaign, 16% during campaign, 12% will decide later. Стored notes also assert wontVote=40. Not directly visible in AR's published summary text."}}, {"id": "ar-2026-03-26", "agencyId": "AR", "fieldwor